              ---DayBreak Boat Control---

	Boats will allow you to move on the virtual water surface of
the Darke Mud world. Movements over the water between the land masses
will require their use 

*General Commands*

-On Deck-
'raise sail','lower sail','raise anchor','lower anchor'
'enter boat','exit boat'

-In Crowsnest-
'check near','check <exit dir>'
This allows you to scan adjancent water rooms for land or other boats

*Movements*

-On Deck-
'sail <dir>'
Direction can be any valid room exit that leads into a water room

-Navigation-

navigate <target>
Target can be any destination that you have a map for.
It returns compass direction and distance to target based
on current position of the boat.
